title: '"the language of parts helps because we do not have to say, I feel angry or afraid orimpatient. Instead, we can say, A minute ago a part of me felt ... "'
pid: b9fcae1d-2d8b-44e6-93d9-67f58851b309
body: |2-
  "the language of parts helps clients and therapists disclose strong feelings that might otherwise be embarrassing or controversial"
